Title: Fischer Express cement cartridge 310ml Grey
Description: Ready to use and paintable, Fischer Express cement is a repairing mortar suitable for everything from renovating masonry and fixing roof tiles to sealing drill holes and general repair work. Practically odour-free and with a stable consistency, this cement is resistant to weather, ageing and UV. Protected against frost down to -15°C in the cartridge, Fischer Express is reusable with no need to add water or pre-mix, saving time and mess and reducing waste. Workable in most weathers, this water-based polymer offers good adhesion on slightly damp substrates and has been designed with the visual appearance of the mortar in mind for a discreet finish.
